<p>
    Runtime implementation of the <a href="/intents/breakpoint/">Breakpoint Intent</a>, mapping semantic step names
    to concrete CSS media queries or container queries and exposing reactive state.
</p>
<p>
    Converts abstract steps (<code>compact</code>, <code>medium</code>, <code>expanded</code>) to pixel/em/rem
    breakpoints based on application configuration. Supports both viewport-level (media queries) and
    component-level (container queries) breakpoints. Exposes a <code>matches()</code> API for components
    to query the active breakpoint at runtime.
</p>